column4: When I run apt-get upgrade it tells me "0 upgraded, 0 newly installed, 0 to remove and 1 not upgraded.", what does this mean 1 not upgraded?  Did I mess something up last time I ran it?
zcat[1] : Is dist-upgrade going to take me to 6.06?  I don't want to run an unstable OS.
if your aptget source.list has dapper as it's repository, yes, if it still says breezy, then no
